| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1890 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4fa4c1ab-f89d-5794-8cc1-7e7272c32182"
